Pasta al Pomodoro

Yield: 2
Time: 2h 30m
Link: Mario's Recipes > https://www.super-mario.example/recipes/pasta-al-pomodoro
Tags: Italian, Pasta

Ingredients
  Pasta
    - pasta: 250 g
  Salsa
    - olive oil: 2 teaspoons
    - onions: 1/2
    - garlic: 1 clove
    - tomatoes, crushed: 1 can (425 ml each)
    - basil
    - salt
    - pepper, black

Instructions
  Pasta
    - Cook the pasta for 10 minutes.
  Salsa
    - Saut√© the onions and garlic in olive oil.
    - Stir in the crushed tomatoes and cook on low heat for 15 minutes.
    - Season to taste with salt and pepper.
    - Stir in the basil.
    - Serve sprinkled with Parmesan cheese.

